<section class="row justify-content-center product-wrapper ambassadors">
    <div class="col-md-6 row select">
        <div class="col-lg-12 text-left">

            <h1 class="text-center">Thanks for being a friend of
                <strong>The Face Pack!</strong></h1>

            <p class="text-center">If you're here, its because we think you are awesome and you might want to help us spread 
                the word about our new sheet, rinse &amp; peel beauty face mask subscription in return for a
                <strong>FREE pack of eight face masks from around the world
                </strong>
                to pamper yourself with (we call it
                <em>The Excellent Eight</em>).</p>
            <p class="text-center">Here's how you can help us out...</p>

            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <h2>Step 1 - Get social</h2>
                    <p>
                        <strong>Like</strong>
                        our
                        <a href="https://www.facebook.com/The-Face-Pack-109050714287104/" target="_blank">
                            <strong>Facebook</strong>
                        </a>
                        and
                        <a href="https://www.instagram.com/the.face.pack/" target="_blank">
                            <strong>Instagram</strong>
                        </a>
                        pages.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <h2>Step 2 - Get your face masks</h2>
                    <p>
                        <strong>Enter your details
                        in the form below </strong> and we'll send out your shiny pack of skin care treats. Don't forget to include your <strong>secret code</strong>
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <h2>Step 3 - Get pampering</h2>
                    <p>Your masks should arrive in a few days, then you can
                        <strong>spend some time pampering yourself</strong>
                        - don't forget to take some pictures or video for the next step...</p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <h2>Step 4 - Get the word out</h2>
                    <p>
                        The most important step - <strong>Share an update with your friends, followers, groups and family</strong>
                        on all your social channels telling them what you think of
                        <strong>The Face Pack</strong>
                        and how they can subscribe.</p> 

                        <p>Include any pictures or video you have taken, link to our
                        <a href="/subscribe">
                            <strong>subscribe</strong>
                        </a>
                        page and include
                        <strong>#thefacepack</strong> and  <strong>#gifted</strong>
                        hashtags.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <h6>Thank you, we couldn't do it without your support! We look forward to seeing your updates and hope you enjoy your masks!</h6>

        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6 text-left">

            <form name="ambassadors" method="POST" data-netlify="true">

                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="name">Name</label>
                    <input type="text" class="form-control" id="name" name="Name" placeholder="Enter your name" required="required">
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="exampleInputEmail1">Email address</label>
                    <input type="email" class="form-control" id="exampleInputEmail1" name="Email" placeholder="Enter your email" required="required">
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="street">Street</label>
                    <input type="text" class="form-control" id="street" name="Address" placeholder="Enter the first line of your address" required="required">
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="city">Town/City</label>
                    <input type="text" class="form-control" id="city" name="Town-City" placeholder="Eg. Glasgow" required="required">
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="region">Region</label>
                    <input type="text" class="form-control" name="Region" id="region" placeholder="Eg. Strathclyde">
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="postcode">Post Code</label>
                    <input type="text" class="form-control" id="postcode" name="Postcode" placeholder="Eg. G99 1ZZ" required="required">
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="secretcode">Secret Code</label>
                    <input type="text" class="form-control" id="secretcode" name="Secret" placeholder="" required="required">
                </div>
                <div class="form-check">
                    <input type="checkbox" class="form-check-input" id="social" name="Liked" required="required">
                    <label class="form-check-label" for="social">&nbsp;I've liked your social pages</label>
                </div>
                <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary btn-block mt-3 send">Send me my face masks!</button>
            </form>

        </div>
        <div id="carousel-thumb" class="carousel slide carousel-fade carousel-thumbnails mt-3 col-md-6" data-ride="carousel">
            <!--Slides-->
            <div class="carousel-inner" role="listbox">
                <div class="carousel-item active">
                    <img class="d-block w-100" src="/img/product/top-down-1.png" alt="Top down view of product">
                </div>
                <div class="carousel-item">
                    <img class="d-block w-100" src="/img/product/holding-1.png" alt="Top down view of product">
                </div>
                <div class="carousel-item">
                    <img class="d-block w-100" src="/img/product/stack-1.png" alt="Top down view of product">
                </div>
                <div class="carousel-item">
                    <img class="d-block w-100" src="/img/product/pic2.jpg" alt="Top down view of product">
                </div>
            </div>
            <!--/.Slides-->
            <!--Controls-->
            <a class="carousel-control-prev" href="#carousel-thumb" role="button" data-slide="prev">
                <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                <span class="sr-only">Previous</span>
            </a>
            <a class="carousel-control-next" href="#carousel-thumb" role="button" data-slide="next">
                <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                <span class="sr-only">Next</span>
            </a>
            <!--/.Controls-->
            <ol class="carousel-indicators">
                <li data-target="#carousel-thumb" data-slide-to="0" class="active">
                    <img class="d-block w-100" src="/img/product/top-down-1.png" alt="Top down view of product"></li>
                <li data-target="#carousel-thumb" data-slide-to="1"><img class="d-block w-100" src="/img/product/holding-1.png" alt="Top down view of product"></li>
                <li data-target="#carousel-thumb" data-slide-to="2"><img class="d-block w-100" src="/img/product/stack-1.png" alt="Top down view of product"></li>
                <li data-target="#carousel-thumb" data-slide-to="3"><img class="d-block w-100" src="/img/product/pic2.jpg" alt="Top down view of product"></li>
            </ol>
        </div>

    </div>
</div>
</section>